review_title: One of the best cars available in Pakistan
review_text: 55 quattro if available is a better buy but I have not had any issues with driving to Islamabad from Lahore occasionally. Dealership staff is excellent and features are superb. If you are able to afford one as a second or third car, there is no better alternative.
